Mbali Khanyile KUTHOLWE isidumbu sendoda (38) ebesinamanxeba amaningi okugwazwa emzimbeni nasekhanda ethempelini lebandla iNazareth Baptist Church elidume ngokuthi ikwaShembe, eWaterloo ngaseVerulam. Onogada benkampani iReaction Unit South Africa (Rusa), bathe bafonelwe izakhamizi ebezicela usizo izolo emini. Okhulumela iRusa uMnuz Prem Balram, uthe bafike bazithela phezu kwesidumbu esontweni lakwaShembe. “Le ndoda iqinisekiswe njengeshonile abezimo eziphuthumayo. Abantu bakule ndawo bsitshele ukuthi indoda ebulewe eyakhona kule ndawo,” kusho uBalram. Okhulumela amaphoyisa, uColonel Thembeka Mbele, uthe kuvulwe icala lokubulala eliphenywa amaphoyisa aseVerulam. Uthe izolo ngo-11 ekuseni, kutholwe isidumbu sendoda ebesinamanxeba okugwazwa emzimbeni ebesisesontweni eWaterloo.